OL,3,CThief detained by ITV's The Bill actor
OL,4,Cjailed for 20 weeks
OL,6,FA "persistent thief" who was arrested
OL,7,Fin Southampton after being detained by
OL,8,Fthe man who played TV copper Pc Reg
OL,9,FHollis has been jailed for 20 weeks.
OL,11,FActor Jeff Stewart, who played Pc
OL,12,FHollis for 24 years in ITV series The
OL,13,FBill, jumped into action after Mohamed
OL,14,FDiallo fell from his bike as he
OL,15,Fattempted to flee after stealing items
OL,16,Ffrom a shop in Southampton, Hampshire.
OL,18,FThe TV star sat on the 29-year-old's
OL,19,Flegs while police officers handcuffed
OL,20,Fhim on July 23.
