OL,6,FDiallo, of Anglesea Road, Southampton,
OL,7,Fwas convicted of seven offences of
OL,8,Ftheft from supermarkets and
OL,9,Fconvenience stores in the Hampshire
OL,10,Fcity between May and July this year.
OL,12,FAt Southampton Magistrates' Court,
OL,13,Fprosecutor Adam Doyle said that Diallo
OL,14,Fhad stolen coffee and alcohol worth a
OL,15,Ftotal of about #314 during the series
OL,16,Fof thefts.
OL,18,FHe added that the defendant had 13
OL,19,Fprevious convictions for a total of 48
OL,20,Foffences including 41 of theft.
