OL,6,FBarry Keel, defending, said that
OL,7,FDiallo had been receiving treatment
OL,8,Ffor alcohol and drug addiction while
OL,9,Fon remand for the offences and added
OL,10,Fthat he hoped to "break the cycle" of
OL,11,Fre-offending.
OL,13,FSentencing Diallo, magistrate Alan
OL,14,FFoster told him: "You are a persistent
OL,15,Fthief with a record that is unenviable.
