OL,6,F"Whatever help we have tried to give
OL,7,Fyou since you have been sentenced
OL,8,Fbefore and currently, you have turned
OL,9,Fit down and you have carried on
OL,10,Fstealing from shops to allow your
OL,11,Fhabit of hard drugs to continue.
OL,13,F"We can find nothing that shows
OL,14,Fremorse on your part, you keep falling
OL,15,Fback into your way of life when even
OL,16,Foffered many opportunities that others
