OL,4,Cjailed for 20 weeks
OL,6,F"Officers making an arrest in
OL,7,FSouthampton were aided by none other
OL,8,Fthan TV's Pc Reg Hollis during an
OL,9,Fincident on Wednesday July 23.
OL,11,F"The officers, from Bargate
OL,12,FNeighbourhoods Policing Team, were in
OL,13,Fthe city in the afternoon when they
OL,14,Fwere alerted by staff at Co-op in
OL,15,FOcean Way to a suspected shoplifter,
OL,16,Fwho attempted to make good his escape
OL,17,Fon a bicycle.
