OL,6,F"The thief, 29-year-old Mohamed
OL,7,FDiallo, fell off the bike during his
OL,8,Fattempts to flee, before officers
OL,9,Fpounced to make their arrest.
OL,11,F"To their surprise, local TV legend
OL,12,FJeff Stewart, who played Pc Hollis for
OL,13,F24 years in The Bill, came to their
OL,14,Faid by sitting on the suspect's legs
OL,15,Fwhile officers put him in cuffs.
OL,17,F"Long since retired from Sun Hill
OL,18,Fstation ` but he's still got it."
